Package networking.types

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AESKeyWrapper
    Used to hold an AESKey
    CredentialsWrapper
    Used to hold the username and password.
    LoginResponseWrapper
    Used to hold the token and whether the client has successfully logged in or not.
    MessageWrapper
    Used to hold a message between two clients.
    ProfileInfoWrapper
    Used to hold all information of an user.
    ProtocolWrapper  
    Request
    This class contains the number of the request,
    which is actually not in use right now,
    the Object which is being buffered,
    and the name of the request (see Requests)
    Response
    This class contains the number of the response,
    which is actually not in use right now,
    the Object which is being buffered,
    and the name of the response (see Responses)
    SearchUserWrapper
    Used to hold a string for autocomplete queries.
    TokenWrapper
    Used to hold a token for the keep logged in feature
    UserVectorWrapper
    Used to hold an vector of users
    Wrapper
    Abstract superclass for wrapper
    Due to not being able to declare a abstract constructor, an constructor containing only the type of String[] is required.
